 _______________________________________________________________________

 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                          MDVA-2009:057
 http://www.mandriva.com/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Package : usermode
 Date    : April 28, 2009
 Affected: 2009.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 A configuration error in usermode was preventing some Mandriva
 graphical tools requiring superuser privileges to be started correctly
 if session was started from KDM.
 
 This updates fixes this issue.
